text: @MartinKuo_ So sorry to hear this Martin. Kindly DM @FedExCanadaHelp your tracking number, full name, address and telephone number, and I will have a look. Thank you.
@MartinKuo_ My apologies @FedExCanada cannot assist with FedEx US Domestic shipments. I will sent your message to our US FedEx Customer Care team @FedExHelp so they can assist you further.
@MitchThinks Hello Mitch, if there is something that we can assist you with, please DM @FedExCanadaHelp your  tracking number, telephone number and complete address.

@ororoiquadi Here is what is showing now. Hi, thank you for getting back to me. I'm a US Social Media Rep and can only assist with packages traveling within the US. Please contact @FedExCanadaHelp for assistance. Rebecc
